        "subject": "LU-19561 rust: Simplify fid resolution in changelog",
        "message": "LU-19561 rust: Simplify fid resolution in changelog\n\nAlways reconstruct path using filename and parent if both are\navaialble. If not then attempt to resolve the full path of the\nfid and fallback to just filename, if it exists.\n\nLong term this conversion logic needs to move out of the api\nand into applications.\n\nSigned-off-by: Robert Read <rread@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Id0d96342fdec7ed496a2a241d395f988ef45556b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
